      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-100 Dummy&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 1 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SGM-1 body, which is a nimble general-purpose missile.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_HEIMPACT warhead.  It homes in on its target using a Semi-Active Radar seeker.

